headline: Arthur J. Gallagher (AJG) Takes Over Michigan Leadership Consultancy
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE:AJG) is one of the top stocks sold by hedge funds. On August 4, AJG confirmed the acquisition of Dion Leadership, Inc. of Novi, Michigan. The financial terms were not shared.
